%% NOTE:
%% This diagram represents a possible future end-to-end receipt-bound
%% execution model where the wallet directly signs intents.
%% It is NOT normative for VFA v0.1.
%%
%% In VFA v0.1, the issuer (not the wallet) signs and mints the visa token.
%% See TOKEN_FORMAT.md and PROTOCOL.md for the normative v0.1 flow.
%%
%% This diagram may be revisited as a future extension in a later version.

sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant W as Wallet
  participant M as Merchant
  participant G as Verification Gateway
  participant B as Backend
  participant A as Audit Log

  U->>M: Request action (e.g. purchase)
  M->>W: Intent request
  Note right of M: {action, params, merchantId,<br/>endpoint, nonce, expiry}

  W->>U: Display human-readable intent
  U->>W: Approve

  W->>W: Sign intent
  Note right of W: intentHash = Hash(canonical(intent))<br/>signature = Sign(intentHash, walletPrivKey)

  W->>M: Signed intent {intent + signature}
  Note right of M: Passthrough only —<br/>no modification permitted.<br/>Gateway rejects any field<br/>not covered by signature.

  M->>G: Submit {intent + signature}

  G->>G: Verify signature
  Note right of G: Verify Sign(intentHash, walletPubKey)
  G->>G: Verify nonce uniqueness
  G->>G: Verify expiry (≤ 60 s)
  G->>G: Verify context binding
  Note right of G: merchantId + endpoint + userId<br/>must match signed payload
  G->>G: Commit intentHash
  Note right of G: Intent commitment —<br/>prevents reinterpretation.<br/>Execution proceeds only<br/>against committed intentHash.

  G->>B: Dispatch execution(intentHash)
  B->>B: Execute operation

  B->>G: Execution receipt
  Note right of B: receipt = Sign(intentHash + result,<br/>backendPrivKey)

  G->>G: Verify receipt binds to committed intentHash
  G->>A: Append audit record
  Note right of A: hash-chain audit log:<br/>{intentHash, receipt, timestamp,<br/>merchantId, userId}

  G->>M: Result + receipt
  M->>W: Return receipt

  W->>W: Verify receipt matches intentHash
  Note right of W: Confirms executed action matches<br/>what the user originally signed.
  W->>U: Display verified result
